metadata.name: DREAMER #0007
metadata.description:
What if I said I was struggling?
And all that you see is a façade?
A glossy veneer
Hiding what's really here

Pain, anguish, anxiety—uncertainty
The never ending questions
Failures, mistakes—lessons
Pyrrhic successes disguised as blessings

The noises continue to deafen
When will the pressure lessen?
